* RadHydroLimiterType (LimType) [3; 0,1,2,3,4]
  - 0 => original Levermore-Pomraning limiter
  - 1 => rational approx. to LP limiter
  - 2 => Reynolds approx. to LP limiter
  - 3 => no limiter
  - 4 => ZEUS limiter
