    efficiency) and simplify interface?
* RadiationBoundaryX*Faces = (BdryType[][]) [0; 0,1,2]
  - 0 => periodic
  - 1 => Dirichlet
  - 2 => Neumann
* RadHydroInitialGuess (initial_guess) [0; 0,5]
  - 0 => previous time step
  - 5 => analytical solution to local physics
